en_4165157_0	MP Sajin De Vass Gunawardena has been questioned by the Commission to Investigate Allegations of Bribery or Corruption.
en_4165157_1	The Bribery Commission said that the statement was recorded from the MP taking a number of complaints that were lodged against him into consideration.
en_4165157_2	This situation was confirmed to News1st by the commissioner of the Bribery commission.
